text:
I am using the POST `/crm/v3/objects/{objectType}` endpoint to create a custom object and I am trying to understand the syntax for how to use the associations parameter in the body.

The `{objectType}` in my particular case is `affiliates` and I am trying to associate it with a standard HubSpot `contact` object (e.g. Affiliate &lt;&gt; Contact). I already have the Record ID - I just can't make sense of this structure/reference in the docs:

```'associations' =&gt; [
  [
    'to' =&gt; [
      'id' =&gt; 'string'
    ],
    'types' =&gt; [
      [
        'associationCategory' =&gt; 'USER_DEFINED',
        'associationTypeId' =&gt; ''
      ]
    ]
  ]
] ```
